- **Cessation Details**:  
  - **33,064 YALAC Performance Share Rights (STIP 2023)** forfeited on 15/07/2025 due to employee resignations.  
  - **71,879 YALAC Performance Share Rights (STIP 2023)** vested on 14/07/2025 and settled via cash payment at **AUD 6.218552 per right**.  

- **Post-Cessation Issued Capital**:  
  - **Ordinary Shares (YAL)**: 1,320,439,437.  
  - **Unquoted Performance Rights**:  
    - YALAC (STIP 2023) balance reduced to 427,578.  
    - Other LTIP/STIP rights remain unchanged (see table in Part 3).  

No material impact on liquidity or capital structure identified.
